caption:
#Contest .
I love you guys . So much , more than words explain .  People judge me
For liking "the magcon boys" but they don't understand how much you've impacted my life . I've been in this fandom for a long time , and I'm not going anywhere ... You guys are special to me whether you know it or not. I mean you're so sweet and talented and good looking and  perfect ... How do you not like that . You can make me happy , when I'm sad . I can depend on it , on the verge of tears I can watch a single vine , or get 4 seconds into one of your song , and know everything's going to be okay . I'm not the most perfect person , not the most good looking but I know one thing for sure , I Love you till the end of the earth and I'll love you forever . I love you in away words can't explain , there Johnson girls , there's Gilinsky girls , me ? I'm neither , I'm a all of the above kinda girl , you both make me extremely happy and I'll support you guys forever . I'll support all of your relationships , your choices because your happiness means a lot too me.  I'm never going to win this contest , so many girls comment . Haha , somehow , I have a little tiny tiny bit of hope , and faith , I basically gave up on meeting you guys , but something , isn't letting me give up completely . Maybe this contest ... Is it , I doubt it ... But who knows .
